{"tid":1169534,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[HR 入] 遞完信之後返唔過10日，應該賠錢定no pay","createTime":"2019-05-24T12:40:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T13:19:44.000Z","uid":253170,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c9b586720459101492c2636268543634055aeb35","tid":1169534,"uid":253170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T12:40:41.000Z","msg":"話說公司就有位好同事，因家裏各人陸續逝世，需要不停請假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後尾唔知係覺得過意唔去定其他因由，咁就自己遞左信<br />\n<br />\n基於 E 位好同事就實在太不幸啦， 除咗家裏各人陸續逝世，意外又接二連三咁發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頭暈身㷫、交通意外、感情問題、財產問題等等...<br />\n<br />\n咁因為事情就接二連三既發生，導致到好同事係最後一個月都見唔到我地幾日<br />\n<br />\n請問各位HR 大哥，E 位好同事佢應該係要賠錢比公司定就咁 NO PAY 算？？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n*公司規矩：離職需要一個月通知期或者補一個月糧*<br />\n<br />\n今個月同好同事相見好似唔過 7 日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：無真正探究過各種意外真假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  或者可能係真既 RIP"},{"pid":"e7a0409228a14c97c320d7d90c3c4476c12b81dd","tid":1169534,"uid":253170,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T12:46:28.000Z","msg":"屌佢老味，食撚曬d 屎<br />\n鍾意就返黎一兩日痾下屎   唔鍾意就掉d 新屎係道<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下個做到你同事真係三生有幸"},{"pid":"656dc39efe0222591f65da806ba892a527d1719f","tid":1169534,"uid":186314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T12:48:11.000Z","msg":"我覺得係no pay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada193b2a10dbb07ed72021fc9379e5e07fbe8cc","tid":1169534,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T12:49:34.000Z","msg":"扣al lo<br />\n無al咪 no pay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22e80b449b7c89ad8678422729ffb8887354bc54","tid":